    <article id="post-5485" class="post-5485 post type-post status-publish format-link has-post-thumbnail hentry category-fema tag-dipp tag-e-commerce-activities tag-fdi-in-e-commerce tag-marketplace-based-model-of-e-commerce post_format-post-format-link">
